 realise you should not invest in ibis vct or any other vct unless you have carefully thought about whether you can afford it and whether it is right for you you should regard an investment in ibis vct or any other vct as a longer term investment we recommend that you seek independent financial advice from an appropriately authorised independent financial adviser as to whether an investment in ibis vct or any other vct is suitable for you as well as your personal entitlement to any tax reliefs associated with an investment in a vct the share price of a vct may not reflect its net asset value investment focus ibis media vct principally invests in smaller unquoted companies although alternative investment market aim listed companies will also be considered ibis media vct will consider providing finance for a range of different situations including expansion capital for fast growing companies looking to develop their business finance for companies looking to make an acquisition mbombi finance for management teams looking to buy a company or business from its existing owners preipo finance for companies preparing to float on the aim the objective of ibis media vct is to develop a balanced investment portfolio that has potential for capital appreciation the characteristics of an investee company can typically be expected to include a sustainable business model competitive advantage a strong management team organic revenue growth potential profitability or the expectation of profitability within a reasonable timeframe in order to mitigate investors’ risk investments in business startups will generally be avoided unless the management team has a strong profile in the media sector and a prior track record of value creation for shareholders current investments contagious business information contagious business information contagious is a bb provider of global intelligence on current marketing techniques via subscription magazine training and eventsclients include some of the world’s leading advertisers wwwcontagiouscom ginx tv content ginx tv content ginx tv is a  video gaming tv channel aired in over  countries and  languages ginx tv also creates video gamerelated programming for global distribution wwwginxtv freshwater marketing services freshwater marketing services freshwater uk is an established pr and marketing services group built through  acquisitions with regional teams operating throughout the uk and ireland wwwfreshwaterukcom get me media marketing services get me media marketing services get me media is a bb media exchange which connects advertisers and agencies with media owners through listings training events and an innovative briefing service wwwgetmemediacom masher content team   ibis media vct’s approach is to use the media expertise and experience of the members of the investment committee and investment adviser to identify review and analyse each opportunity we believe that to understand the particular dynamics of a business you need the specialist knowledge of the market in which it operates investment advisers david forster cofounder ibis private equity partners llp david forster cofounder ibis capital partner ibis private equity partners llp davidforsteribiscapitalcouk     8 david began his career in media with news group newspapers the uks largest newspaper publisher where he was advertising research manager david then worked for a number of major investment banks as an equity analyst specialising in media including kleinwort benson merrill lynch and salomon smith barney where he was a managing director for  years to  he was cohead of the no  ranked uk media equity research team before taking over responsibility for ssbs global media research product in  he left ssb and after completing an advisory project for wpp group he set up ibis capital with charles mcintyre charles mcintyre cofounder ibis private equity llp charles mcintyre cofounder ibis capital partner ibis private equity partners llp cmibiscapcom     